org.cyclops.integrateddynamics.core.block

Interface ICollidable.IComponent<P,B>

  • Type Parameters:
    P - The type of positions this component type can provide.
    B - The type of block this component is part of.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CollidableComponentCableCenter, CollidableComponentCableConnections, CollidableComponentFacade, CollidableComponentParts
    Enclosing interface:
    ICollidable<P>

    public static interface ICollidable.IComponent<P,B>
    A component that can be part of the collision detection for a block.
